values_function_receives_buffered_snapshot|add_function_value|0|1
values_function_receives_buffered_snapshot|add_function_value|0|2
values_function_receives_buffered_snapshot|add_function_value|0|3
values_function_receives_buffered_snapshot|add_function_value|0|4
values_function_receives_buffered_snapshot|add_function_value|0|5
values_function_receives_buffered_snapshot|start
values_function_receives_buffered_snapshot|expect_sent_count|1|5
values_function_receives_buffered_snapshot|expect_payload_contains|0|"Value":15

values_function_cache_evicts_oldest|create_collector
values_function_cache_evicts_oldest|create_values_function_int_sum_sensor|contract/func/evict|60000|3
values_function_cache_evicts_oldest|add_function_value|0|1
values_function_cache_evicts_oldest|add_function_value|0|2
values_function_cache_evicts_oldest|add_function_value|0|3
values_function_cache_evicts_oldest|add_function_value|0|4
values_function_cache_evicts_oldest|add_function_value|0|5
values_function_cache_evicts_oldest|start
values_function_cache_evicts_oldest|expect_sent_count|1|5
values_function_cache_evicts_oldest|expect_payload_contains|0|"Value":12

